<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="What_Exactly_is_War.3F">What Exactly is War?</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Outline_of_war&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: What Exactly is War?">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>War can be described as all of the following:</p>
<ul>
