<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Military_tactics">Military tactics</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Outline_of_war&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Military tactics">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
